[space]+mouse :roatae view
z+mouse       : zoom
.+mouse  : center screen at pt
s+mouse  : shows closest corner
c        : set current corner
[number]+mouse  : move numbered spheres

v+mouse : move the vertex in a plane parallel to screen
d+mouse : change vertex depth

Y : refines mesh
N : next corner
P : prev corner
S : swing
U : unswing
L : left
R : right
O : opposite corner

G : circulates through meshes
] : recenters the model
= : toggle transparency
- : toggle edge view
_ : toggle flat shading/smooth shading
| : show normals
x+mouse : delete triangle
` : recompute mesh, shows a red boundary
/ : edge flip
B : smooth 
p : computes path from seed to current corner
